      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get that, but i'm super busy this week and an urgent care trip is a huge hassle. it doesn't feel that bad, just a bit annoying. couldn't i just try some of those redness relief drops (like visine) for a day or two to see if it goes down on its own? if it's an infection, wouldn't it just clear up once the irritation is gone?",
